pageContext.description: Cutting edge chipped and blunt; faces quite plain and without ribs; much of socket partly chipped; inside of socket shows a rib going down the centre of one face, and has traces of wood.
pageContext.surface: Smooth, but slightly rough on the loop side
pageContext.associations: Part of a large hoard; see card for first socketed celt.
